summary: I have a solid foundation in HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, and Tailwind, complemented by ongoing learning in Data Structures and Algorithms (DSA) with Java. I’m currently focused on mastering front-end development with JavaScript and plan to leverage my Java skills for back-end development. My goal is to advance into full-stack development, combining my front-end expertise with a strong back-end foundation. In addition to my technical skills, I possess strong leadership qualities, effective communication, problem-solving abilities, and a collaborative mindset. These soft skills enable me to work effectively in team environments, manage projects efficiently, and adapt to challenges in dynamic settings.

projects.name: Bootstrap InfoPage
projects.description: Developed a fully responsive informational web page using the Bootstrap framework. The project includes a sidebar menu, responsive navbar, and various forms, showcasing my skills in creating adaptable and user-friendly web designs.
